  "code": "---\nconfig:\n  theme: redux\n  flowchart:\n    curve: basis\n    nodeSpacing: 60\n    rankSpacing: 85\n    padding: 10\n  themeVariables:\n    fontFamily: ''\n    fontSize: 16px\n    lineColor: '#333333'\n    textColor: '#111111'\n  layout: dagre\n  look: neo\n---\nflowchart LR\n    Shift[\"Cost-shifting game\"] --> Place[\"Placement game\"] & Press[\"Pressure (public signal)\"]\n    Place --> Press\n    Press --> Risk[\"Clinical risk\"] & Signal[\"Signalling game\"]\n    Signal --> Barg[\"Bargaining game\"]\n    Risk --> Signal\n    Define[\"Definition game\"] --> Barg\n    Code[\"Coding game\"] --> Define\n    Audit[\"Compliance game\"] --> Define\n    Bail[\"Bailout game\"] --> Barg\n    Barg --> Bail\n    Integr[\"Integration game\"] --> Shift & Risk\n    Press -.-> Audit\n    Audit -.-> Press\n\n     Barg:::g\n     Signal:::g\n     Define:::g\n     Shift:::g\n     Place:::g\n     Code:::g\n     Audit:::g\n     Bail:::g\n     Integr:::g\n     Press:::o\n     Risk:::o\n    classDef g fill:#DFF1FF,stroke:#0B5FA5,stroke-width:1.8px,color:#111,rx:14,ry:14\n    classDef o fill:#FFE0E0,stroke:#B23B3B,stroke-width:2.6px,color:#111,rx:14,ry:14\n    style Press fill:#FFD1D1,stroke:#8F1F1F,stroke-width:3px",
