  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗政策博弈的流程图，核心是成本转移博弈（Cost-shifting game）作为起点，然后分出两条线：一个是安置博弈，另一个是公共信号压力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Shift节点要指向Place和Press两个节点。那Place和Press之间有关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "有的，安置博弈会产生压力，所以Place要指向Press。然后Press再往下分：一边是临床风险，另一边是信号博弈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Press连接到Risk和Signal了。接下来Signal往哪走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "信号博弈会导向议价博弈（Bargaining game）。另外，临床风险和信号博弈之间是双向的——风险会触发信号，信号也会反过来影响风险认知。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Signal指向Barg，Risk和Signal互相连接，记下了。那议价博弈还有什么上游节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "定义博弈（Definition game）也会指向议价博弈，这是政策制定层面的。然后编码博弈（Coding game）和合规审计（Compliance game）都指向定义博弈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Code和Audit都指向Define，然后Define指向Barg。还有一个Bailout game，它和Bargaining game是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "救助博弈和议价博弈是双向的——议价失败可能导致救助，救助机制又会影响下一轮议价策略。所以Barg和Bail互相指向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "双向箭头加上了。还有一个Integration game，它应该连到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Integr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "整合博弈是宏观层面的，它同时影响成本转移博弈和临床风险，所以Integr要指向Shift和Risk。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Shift",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Integr到Shift和Risk的连接完成了。我注意到Press和Audit之间是不是也有关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Shift",
        "Risk",
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，压力和合规审计是互相影响的，用虚线双向连接表示这种反馈关系，不是直接的因果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Press和Audit之间的虚线双向连接已添加。现在我们来处理样式吧。哪些节点用蓝色系，哪些用红色系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "博弈类节点用蓝色：Barg、Signal、Define、Shift、Place、Code、Audit、Bail、Integr都用g类样式。压力和风险这两个是外部驱动因素，用红色系o类样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Signal",
        "Define",
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Integr",
        "Press",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。Press和Risk用o类红色，其他博弈节点用g类蓝色。Press需要特殊强调吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Pressure是核心公共信号，需要更深的红色填充和更粗的边框来突出。用#FFD1D1填充，#8F1F1F描边，3px线宽。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Press的特殊样式已设置。g类的具体参数呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "g类用#DFF1FF填充，#0B5FA5描边，1.8px线宽，文字颜色#111，圆角14px。o类用#FFE0E0填充，#B23B3B描边，2.6px线宽，同样圆角14px。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "g",
        "o"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两个classDef都配置好了。我检查一下整体布局：从左到右，Integr在左上连到Shift和Risk，Shift分出Place和Press，Press往下到Risk和Signal，Signal到Barg，Risk和Signal互连，Define连Barg，Code和Audit连Define，Barg和Bail互连，Press和Audit虚线互连。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Shift",
        "Risk",
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Define",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构是对的。不过我刚才想了一下，Audit到Press的虚线方向，是不是画成双向更合适？我之前说的互相影响，用两个单向虚线还是一条双向虚线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Mermaid里可以用-.-表示无向虚线，或者两个方向各画一条。您想要明确的双向箭头还是无向的互连？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "用无向虚线就可以了，-.-这种，表示它们之间有反馈关系但不强调方向。另外，我刚才漏说了，Place到Press应该是实线有向的，这个没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认，Place到Press是实线箭头，Audit和Press之间改成无向虚线-.-。还有其他需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没有了，这个结构完整呈现了医疗政策中从成本转移、信号传递到最终议价和救助的完整博弈链条。颜色和线宽区分也很清楚，可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Define",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Integr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
